{"tid":1778925,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美前國安揭中共威脅 「傾全力打壓普世價值」","createTime":"2019-12-11T10:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T11:29:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb2f12cc40662929b27c7ab18b556439e802ee5","tid":1778925,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191211/G2KIHCDJTUJGBLS3D6V723YERA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191211%2FG2KIHCDJTUJGBLS3D6V723YERA%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwpFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=9ef896ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191211%2FG2KIHCDJTUJGBLS3D6V723YERA%2F&h=b525d79b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191211/G2KIHCDJTUJGBLS3D6V723YERA/</a><br />\n<br />\n美前國安揭中共威脅<br />\n「傾全力打壓普世價值」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191211/large/1575993710_1d58.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191211%2Flarge%2F1575993710_1d58.gif&h=b14099b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《隱蔽的戰爭》詳細講述中共對美構成的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n除了美國前CIA出書大爆中共間諜內幕，美國前白宮國家安全委員會高級主任史帕丁（Robert Spalding III）近日也出版新書《隱蔽的戰爭：中國如何在美國精英熟睡時進行趕超？》，內容指中共是美國最大的威脅，因中共會盡全力打壓美國尊崇的普世價值，例如人權、民主、自由，而華府朝野也越來越多人意識到，中共對民主本身就是威脅。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：情報思維僵化 賴美反送中推手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華府朝野「覺醒」<br />\n<br />\n史帕丁在新書中表示，中共認為一些普世價值，其實都是要推翻共產黨，所以中共一直都傾全力在中國及其他國家打壓這些價值。而在美國，都有越來越多人意識到中共是對民主的威脅。史帕丁指自己在2014年的時候，就已開始揭示中共對美國金融、投資，以及媒體、政治、網絡等領域的影響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，從經濟角度來看，他指中國進入世界貿易組織（WTO）後，美國在2001年至2017年間失去7,000多家工廠，他認為中國應基於自由貿易原則，遵守國際規定，而美國亦應以中國入世貿前的做法應對，讓國會每年審批中國是否達到市場經濟標準，有否違反人權原則等。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"11b8ca597e7b441de40193a27c5dd21e26fe2e6f","tid":1778925,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7bddd93f9196d703cce4c940b78f5c490ba358e","tid":1778925,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢搬返麥卡錫主義出黎都唔過份，係有幾多共諜先可以令到美國水魚咁任人劏"},{"pid":"d4aafa3ce27e3f2929c81910ca92bf77709d5db5","tid":1778925,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"世界要醒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a1ca342550bf830e87efa5f1e6145f391b983b","tid":1778925,"uid":53411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"「覺醒」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5badba442199f19e85ca3b23bbe1cad5213826b8","tid":1778925,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"傾全力打壓普世價值<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂，好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce42d396de2870515b9ed1cfdcb0dcbb057d5530","tid":1778925,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}